Caption: Dr. h. c. Heinrich Luebke, President of the Federal Republic of Germany, meets some of the personalities at IIT Madras
Description: Dr. Luebke shakes hands with Mrs. Shanti Sengupto (in white sari). Prof. B. Sengupto (on Dr. Luebke's left), Dr.Koch (fifth from left), Mrs. Koch (fourth from left) and Prof. Krishnamurthy are also present.
